### Frontend Override Rule (critical)

Three layers, three placement rules:

- Change existing CRM component/page → `frontend/src_override/<same path as upstream>`
- Add brand-new component/page → `frontend/src/...`
- Sidebar → `frontend/src/index.js` `customSidebarItems`

Never edit `crm_build/` (wiped on every build) or `apps/crm/frontend/src/` (upstream). Run `yarn check-conflicts` after CRM updates.
